data.description: Start the NEW YEAR in the PERFECT HOUSE in the PERFECT LOCATION! The meticulously maintained property has undergone significant upgrades….air conditioner (2018), water heater (2018), wood floors (2018), roof (2020), new siding with new house wrap (2023), new shutters (2023), and a FINISHED basement (2023). The “heavy lifting” has been done, so you can simply move in and start enjoying your new home.  All of this adds up to THE BEST HOUSE VALUE ON THE MARKET IN WALDORF! Step inside to discover a cozy yet elegant formal living room and dining room with upgraded hardwood floors, adding a touch of refinement to the living spaces. The open kitchen and family room grace the rear of the house, providing the ideal space for daily family living. The FINISHED basement offers a versatile space for relaxing or entertaining. Upstairs your spacious primary suite welcomes you home with a renovated, spa-style  bath, adding a touch of luxury to your daily routine. The walk-in closet with closet system is every fashionable owner’s dream. Three additional, generously-sized bedrooms provide ample space for children or a comfy retreat for your guests. The house sits on one of the largest lots in the neighborhood, just under a half acre, ensuring a private and spacious oasis for you to enjoy. The fenced yard with deck adds an extra layer of privacy, making it perfect for both relaxation and outdoor activities. The convenient location near shopping and schools, is perfectly situated between Rt. 210 and Rt. 301/Branch Ave, ensuring an easy commute. Don't miss the chance to start the new year in your new home, where all the essential upgrades have been taken care of. Schedule a visit today and experience the comfort and convenience this property has to offer!
